# Summary
Amplitude Activation's Recommendations feature uses AutoML to determine which items are most likely to drive users toward a predictive goal by clustering users based on properties and behaviors, analyzing historical data, and generating personalized ranked item lists that update hourly, best suited for user-based personalization in ecommerce, marketplace, B2C, and subscription software companies.

